# üêµ KUAPE Tokenomics

We took one of our favorites coin SafeMoon and SUSHI, and used it as the basis for our tokenomics. We made some alterations along the way to better suit our vision, keep things fresh and original, and improve the economics around the token.

Compared to others like Sushi or Cake, KUS doesn't have an infinite supply. Compared to Safemoon we have fixed supply, static reward and automatic liquidity pool. 

**The tokenomics of KUAPE can be broken down in the following way:**

* KUAPE employs 3 simple functions: Reflection + LP acquisition + Burn In each trade, the transaction is taxed a 9% fee, which is split 3 ways.
  * 3% fee = redistributed to all existing holders 
  * 3% fee is split 50/50 half of which is sold by the contract into KCS, while the other half of the KUAPE tokens are paired automatically with the previously mentioned KCS and added as a liquidity pair on KuApeDEX. 
  * 3% fee will be sent to burn wallet \(0x000000000000000000000000000000000000dEaD\)
* Fixed total supply \(350,000,000 KUAPE\).
* 10 KUAPE is released per block and reward to farmer LP our token. 
* Up to 100% of the exchange trade fees are awarded to holders in the form of KUAPE tokens \(for selected pairs\).
* 50% of swap fees are reserved for a scheduled buyback of the KUAPE token for burning, and the remaining 50% go to development.

Our goal is to come up with the most fair and equal distribution of the token supply so that early holders are heavily rewarded, while at the same time creating strong incentives for long term growth, encouraging new investors to join our ecosystem.

**This is the breakdown of the KUAPE supply:**

* 350,000,000 ‚Üí Total supply/hardcap
  * 345,000,000 ‚Üí Farming \(will be mint 10 KUAPE per block\)
  * 5,000,000 -&gt; Initial Supply
    * 1,000,000 ‚Üí Team tokens, locked and vested for 24 months \(KUAPE foundation\)
    * 1,000,000 ‚Üí Locked and vested for 24 months for listing, marketing and partnerships
    * 2,000,000 ‚Üí Presale 
    * 700,000 ‚Üí Initial Liquidity
    * 300,000 ‚Üí Future Contests ie. Trading Contests
